data.description: Nestled amongst the serene landscape sits this Beautiful 11acre, 4 Bdrm, 2.5 Bath home located in the Beaver LSD, Calcutta. Follow the Beautiful Tree-Lined Drive to this Well Maintained home boasting a 2 Car Attached Garage and 2 Car Detached Garage. The 30x26 Detached Garage boasts a 30x16 unfinished 2nd Level that would be perfect as a Wood Shop, Yoga Studio or Game Rm. A Metal Roof, 200amp Electrical panel and Underground transformer, so there are no exposed wires, complete the space. The quiet serenity and beauty of this property makes one feel like your in a wooded oasis, but a quick drive to Golf, Shopping and Dining. Step inside and be greeted by a Large Living Rm. The Eat In Kitchen boasts Granite Countertops, Stone Backsplash and Built in Cabinet complete with Wine Rack. The LR offers a Gas Propane Fireplace and leads to the DR. Perfect for casual gatherings. The rear FR is perfect space for TV, Game Rm or Office Space and boasts Vaulted Ceilings. French Doors from the FR lead to your backyard oasis. Imagine the Sunlight dancing on the surface of the 36x18 in-ground pool. Lounge poolside under the warm sun, listening to the gentle rustling of the trees and the sweet chirping of the birds. As evening settles in, string some patio lights and gather around the pool for stargazing under a sky unpolluted by city lights. The 2nd level boasts a Primary Suite with 2 Walk-in Closets and a 3 piece Tiled On-Suite. The Lower Level Basement features a Bonus space with Wood Burning FP, Laundry and a space perfect for an Office, Craft Rm or Game Rm. You do not want to miss the 2 piece lower level bath. This home seamlessly blends the charm of country living but with the modern comforts. Offering Privacy, tranquility, and endless opportunities for creating cherished memories!
